# Keep host build artefacts out of the image context so the image installs/builds
# its own (correct-arch) deps and dist. node_modules especially must NOT leak in
# (host bcrypt is built for the host OS/arch).
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.env
.env.*
*.log
coverage
**/coverage
